    {
      "name": "Jobs REST",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "POST /api/jobs/search - Basic JSON",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200 o 201', function () {",
                  "  pm.expect([200, 201]).to.include(pm.response.code);",
                  "});",
                  "pm.test('Respuesta con count y jobs', function () {",
                  "  var body = pm.response.json();",
                  "  pm.expect(body).to.have.property('count');",
                  "  pm.expect(body).to.have.property('jobs');",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "key": "x-api-key",
                "value": "{{apiKey}}",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "description": "Busqueda REST principal.\n\nQuery params soportados:\n- `format`: `json` o `csv`\n- `paginate`: `true|false`\n- `page`: numero de pagina\n- `page_size`: tamano de pagina (1-100)\n\nBody (`ScraperInputDto`) soportado:\n- `siteType[]`: fuentes a consultar\n- `searchTerm`: termino de busqueda\n- `googleSearchTerm`: override especifico para Google\n- `location`: ubicacion\n- `distance`: radio en millas\n- `isRemote`: solo remotos\n- `jobType`: `fulltime|parttime|contract|temporary|internship|perdiem|nights|other|summer|volunteer`\n- `easyApply`: filtra easy apply\n- `resultsWanted`: cantidad deseada\n- `offset`: offset interno del scraper\n- `hoursOld`: antiguedad maxima en horas\n- `country`: enum de pais, por ejemplo `USA`, `UK`, `SPAIN`, `GERMANY`\n- `descriptionFormat`: `markdown|html|plain`\n- `linkedinFetchDescription`: trae descripcion completa en LinkedIn\n- `linkedinCompanyIds[]`: ids de compania para LinkedIn\n- `requestTimeout`: timeout en segundos\n- `proxies[]`: lista de proxies\n- `caCert`: ruta a certificado CA\n- `userAgent`: user agent custom\n- `clientIp`: IP cliente para ciertas fuentes\n- `enforceAnnualSalary`: normaliza salarios a anual\n- `rateDelayMin`, `rateDelayMax`: throttling entre requests\n- `companySlug`: requerido por fuentes ATS\n- `maxConcurrentCompanies`: concurrencia ATS\n- `retries`, `retryDelay`, `retryBackoff`, `retryMaxDelay`: politicas de retry\n- `auth`: credenciales por fuente\n\nBloque `auth` soportado:\n- `upwork`: `grantType`, `clientId`, `clientSecret`, `accessToken`, `refreshToken`\n- `usajobs`: `apiKey`, `email`\n- `adzuna`: `appId`, `appKey`\n- `reed`: `apiKey`\n- `jooble`: `apiKey`\n- `careerjet`: `affId`\n- `exa`: `apiKey`\n- `greenhouse`: `apiKey`\n- `lever`: `apiKey`\n- `ashby`: `apiKey`\n- `smartrecruiters`: `apiKey`\n- `workable`: `accessToken`, `subdomain`\n- `teamtailor`: `apiToken`\n- `recruitee`: `apiToken`\n- `bamboohr`: `apiKey`\n- `personio`: `clientId`, `clientSecret`\n- `jazzhr`: `apiKey`\n- `jobvite`: `apiKey`, `apiSecret`\n- `trakstar`: `apiKey`\n- `deel`: `apiToken`\n- `loxo`: `apiToken`\n- `fountain`: `apiKey`\n- `bullhorn`: `corpToken`\n\nUsa `GraphQL / listSources` para ver el enum completo de `siteType`.",
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"searchTerm\": \"{{searchTerm}}\",\n  \"siteType\": [\"{{sitePrimary}}\"],\n  \"resultsWanted\": {{resultsWanted}},\n  \"location\": \"{{location}}\",\n  \"country\": \"{{country}}\",\n  \"descriptionFormat\": \"markdown\",\n  \"isRemote\": true\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/jobs/search",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "jobs",
                "search"
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "POST /api/jobs/search - Paginated",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200 o 201', function () {",
                  "  pm.expect([200, 201]).to.include(pm.response.code);",
                  "});",
                  "pm.test('Respuesta paginada', function () {",
                  "  var body = pm.response.json();",
                  "  pm.expect(body).to.have.property('total_pages');",
                  "  pm.expect(body).to.have.property('current_page');",
                  "  pm.expect(body).to.have.property('page_size');",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "key": "x-api-key",
                "value": "{{apiKey}}",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "description": "Mismo endpoint de busqueda con paginacion REST via query string.",
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"searchTerm\": \"{{searchTerm}}\",\n  \"siteType\": [\"{{sitePrimary}}\", \"{{siteSecondary}}\"],\n  \"resultsWanted\": 10,\n  \"location\": \"{{location}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/jobs/search?paginate=true&page=1&page_size={{pageSize}}",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "jobs",
                "search"
              ],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "paginate",
                  "value": "true"
                },
                {
                  "key": "page",
                  "value": "1"
                },
                {
                  "key": "page_size",
                  "value": "{{pageSize}}"
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "POST /api/jobs/search - CSV Export",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
